Key Match Events: Randal Kolo Muani scored one and assisted another as France celebrated a 3-2 friendly victory over Chile.
Marcelino Nunez scored the opening goal for Chile.
Youssouf Fofana scored the equalizer for France with a deflected effort.
Theo Hernandez assisted Randal Kolo Muani's goal.
Eduardo Vargas hit the post with a free header for Chile.
Randal Kolo Muani assisted Olivier Giroud for his 57th France goal.
Dario Osorio scored a long-range goal for Chile.
Pre-Game Insights: Kylian Mbappe predicted he would be booed by the fans, but he wasn't.
Post-Match Reflections: Didier Deschamps will be considering Randal Kolo Muani's performance for the Euro 2024 squad.
